{"tid":718820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好嘔心","createTime":"2018-06-27T03:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T16:00:16.000Z","uid":33939,"like":34,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7b654482bf6f4056f80495e40c9a2b4052891501","tid":718820,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"有好嘢爭住認，喬寶寶張敬軒果d擁護普世價值，就話佢哋真正香港人。平時就盲反大陸人，南亞人(雖然喬寶寶唔係南亞)。<br />\n<br />\n問題係香港人本身都好多人好劣質。早兩日我返屋企時，經過樓下大閘，咁我本身個人都過咗大半，但見後面一段距離仲有人就停晌度推住道閘，如事者有三個人入咗嚟，冇一個講唔該。即係我唔係要咩回報，又唔係話自己好偉大，而係我去酒店bellboy幫我推門我都會講thank you，我去買嘢/食飯，俾錢都會講唔該。<br />\n<br />\n香港人幾時先會做好自己先？"},{"pid":"29efee49c5134db924b6d8d09d0cb010cae49422","tid":718820,"uid":4845,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"是但啦 我都係好多時推住閘比人入<br />\n有唔該咪微笑下 冇咪由佢"},{"pid":"747b0192f838347c6ea5bd75eb5fd67ed17a08ac","tid":718820,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"我次次幫人推閘對方都會唔該我<br />\n<br />\n咁又點計?"},{"pid":"7bc3ea45e2f5a9bc4caa4c14f1b657265343e53a","tid":718820,"uid":191338,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"按比例而言私樓啲人有禮貌多"},{"pid":"e35915cede5a89b717183e2c094b9579cb27fafa","tid":718820,"uid":37220,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"係兒登講無用<br />\n一陣成班人入黎咬你"},{"pid":"6a38d1837f67486890340a74161aaedf7256922f","tid":718820,"uid":172248,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"這就是香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3226e0b18ae8d8f1b1bed82e0fb8aec859305f","tid":718820,"uid":130897,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:30:31.000Z","msg":"你都係"},{"pid":"a99e97171de7918524dcd1c04fde6f70a15304a1","tid":718820,"uid":33939,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"曾經我晌IFC見過有一對老人家，個阿伯晌IFC去恒生總行條天橋個出口幫人hold住度門，之後個阿婆鬧佢話做乜咁好心，你睇下d人一句唔該都冇。<br />\n<br />\n哩件事令我印度好深刻。"},{"pid":"b9985c90bbaba14f14a2ed5fbacaf9850b6aa618","tid":718820,"uid":166462,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"做下服務業/零售業<br />\n你就知香港人真最垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff41b3c3bfe3e272d413bd8f6f43ba9b69d3015","tid":718820,"uid":707,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"你呢種人仲嘔心<br />\n係真心幫人就唔求回報啦<br />\n同樓上一樣，你地有講唔該咪笑一笑冇咪冇<br />\n咩都計較住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2706da05957ef5b78051ccc434adf80a60ec45df","tid":718820,"uid":133518,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"施恩莫望報"},{"pid":"f3038eadda3d4a4f4e1abea6ee7a1abd01f32ff5","tid":718820,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"做好自己就夠<br />\n成日少少野又開post 香港人xxx"},{"pid":"f23de52f19c4c0c9c92bdb35a2c056fea60877d4","tid":718820,"uid":36058,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2706da05957ef5b78051ccc434adf80a60ec45df","tid":718820,"uid":133518,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"施恩莫望報"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"講聲唔該都算「報」？"},{"pid":"b42608913800ce777a05205a6cd2a6c6bf09c18a","tid":718820,"uid":160263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"尤其啲廢中大部分其實同支那狗冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e423527b4b81d26b7f6d9594db2e6aaac1da81","tid":718820,"uid":171058,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e35915cede5a89b717183e2c094b9579cb27fafa","tid":718820,"uid":37220,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"係兒登講無用<br />\n一陣成班人入黎咬你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"咬緊啦<br />\n成日話日本人幾好幾好，大陸L學唔到<br />\n但一講到